long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
When searching for software development related content, get rid of poor quality domains from your search results in one click.

This extension uses an open source domain whitelist focused on development sites, to filter out poor quality domains from your search results.

All you have to do is search the web as you normally would, then click the "Clean my Results" button and voil√†! Your results only contain quality sources.

It works with both G Search and DuckDuckGo.
